1
00:00:11,360 --> 00:00:11,890
Let's go.

2
00:00:12,520 --> 00:00:13,000
Get up.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,520
Why did you come back?

4
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:15,920
Get up.

5
00:00:16,239 --> 00:00:16,960
Get up.

6
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:20,320
Are you crazy?

7
00:00:32,080 --> 00:00:35,200
Cao Aiyuan, you will regret this.

8
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,200
You still owe me.

9
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:39,800
You can't die.

10
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:43,400
Okay.

11
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:45,200
I owe you.

12
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:08,200
We're here.

13
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,200
Hold on.

14
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,200
Sir.

15
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:22,480
Sir.

16
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:26,600
Who is it?

17
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,080
I'm Huazi.

18
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:31,200
The shop is closed.

19
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,479
There is no food left.

20
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,280
Go somewhere else.

21
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,039
Let's go.

22
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,600
Go.

23
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,800
Is it them?

24
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,160
Yes.

25
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,440
It's these three.

26
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:09,160
These two bastards in front call the one in the back 'boss'.

27
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:11,160
He's the one who chopped off my hand.

28
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,080
What about her?

29
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:15,080
I'd recognize this woman even if she turned to ashes.

30
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,160
She's the one who seduced me.

31
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,880
Anything else to add?

32
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,720
Or did you hear

33
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,640
them mention any other information?

34
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,280
Nothing.

35
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:25,400
Come here. Help me up.

36
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:30,840
Be gentle.

37
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,120
Don't you know I'm injured?

38
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,480
Can you take care of me or not?

39
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,810
If not, get a caregiver.

40
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,400
All our savings were robbed.

41
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,130
We have to be frugal from now on.

42
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,610
I'm telling you,

43
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,720
go back to your parents for money

44
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,920
to treat my injuries.

45
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,840
Why are you so loud?

46
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,600
My ears are ringing.

47
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,200
What was his name?

48
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,240
Hong what?

49
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:51,900
Hong Jinyi.

50
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:53,680
Hong Jinyi.

51
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,770
Your daughter is sitting right there.

52
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,040
Look at yourself.

53
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:00,440
Do you look like a father?

54
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:06,460
Yao Shufen, please come out for a moment.

55
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:21,040
Nuannuan still isn't talking.

56
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:26,880
Nuannuan.

57
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,880
Your little bear is so cute.

58
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,800
How about I give you a present?

59
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,600
Come see.

60
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:39,200
Stickers. There are

61
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:42,200
pink, purple, green, and blue butterflies.

62
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,400
Which one do you like?

63
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,840
Here.

64
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:54,520
Wow, it's so pretty.

65
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:55,800
When your classmates see this,

66
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,080
they will definitely like it.

67
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:59,340
They'll all say your hands are so pretty.

68
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,400
I'll give these to you.

69
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,040
Let Mom help you put them on.

70
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,120
Come.

71
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,960
All right, Director Wang.

72
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,480
Please don't be mad.

73
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,340
I will definitely reprimand him.

74
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,120
Rest assured.

75
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,040
Okay.

76
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:32,240
Hello, Chudong Municipal Public Security Bureau.

77
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,120
This is Li Zheng from Guangnan Sub-bureau.

78
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,720
Please get Ma Guodong for me.

79
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,280
Sir, it's for you.

80
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:39,680
For me?

81
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,960
Who is calling here?

82
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:44,800
Captain Li.

83
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:49,200
Ma Guodong, you think you're so tough.

84
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:52,080
Abusing your power and entering someone else's jurisdiction.

85
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,400
Just because you were dragging your feet,

86
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:55,040
it caused another victim.

87
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,640
Do you know what you have done?

88
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,000
You are just messing around.

89
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,880
Aren't we looking for the suspect?

90
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,200
We will have clues soon.

91
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:04,400
I order you to report back within 24 hours to receive your punishment.

92
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,800
As the squadron leader, I order you, the deputy leader,

93
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,280
to obey your superior's command.

94
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,340
Do you understand?

95
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:13,000
Okay, we'll go back immediately, Captain Li.

96
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,800
Our work in Chudong has to come to an end.

97
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,120
You heard him.

98
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,080
Captain Li told us to hurry back.

99
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:23,880
No, if we put

100
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:26,000
these clues together, we'll have new ones soon.

101
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,000
I know.

102
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,600
But he gave an order.

103
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:33,120
Hurry up, pack your bags and let's go immediately.

104
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,140
Nan C-26179

105
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,850
No, I need to get off.

106
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,000
We haven't reached the station yet.

107
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:07,880
Let's go back to the station first.

108
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:10,040
What's the difference of one day?

109
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,970
They might run away in just one day.

110
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:14,200
Isn't it the same if we go back to the station and then come back to investigate?

111
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,000
Go back yourself if you want to.

112
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,440
I'll investigate on my own.

113
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,520
How will you investigate?

114
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,000
This is a cross-provincial case.

115
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,120
Do you have the paperwork?

116
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:22,720
Besides, can you guarantee you'll catch them?

117
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:27,000
They've already got their hands on a lot of dirty money.

118
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,840
What if they run away with the money?

119
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,640
We won't be able to catch them even if we want to.

120
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:33,120
We've already caught Wu Zhaoxiang. Isn't it the same if we go back and interrogate him first?

121
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,440
He's not the prime culprit.

122
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:37,100
I'm telling you, being so impulsive won't help.

123
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:43,640
Ma Guodong, if you still consider yourself a cop,

124
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,180
don't hold me back anymore, okay?

125
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,680
I'm holding you back?

126
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,520
I've been a cop for 20 years.

127
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,040
Do I always just do the bare minimum to close a case?

128
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,920
Do you think I can't tell?

129
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:56,280
Every time you handle a case, you just do the bare minimum and that's it.

130
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,320
I'm not like you.

131
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,000
How are you different?

132
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,640
You just want to play the hero,

133
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:05,500
and get a First-Class Merit to satisfy your vanity.

134
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,400
I'm trying to satisfy my vanity?

135
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:09,200
Aren't you?

136
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,240
Ma Guodong, let me ask you,

137
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:16,200
you keep saying seeing Nuannuan reminds you of Yinuo and makes your heart ache for her.

138
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,200
How does it ache?

139
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,280
Eating a bowl of noodles before a case,

140
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:22,340
and then the criminals go scot-free?

141
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:24,040
Isn't it ridiculous?

142
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:27,720
Don't you just want to inherit your brother's badge number?

143
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,720
I think you're even more ridiculous.

144
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,640
Don't think I don't know how you got your Second-Class Merit.

145
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:34,280
You got lucky like a blind cat finding a dead mouse.

146
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:36,480
I really feel ashamed for your brother.

147
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:40,659
A cop like you doesn't deserve to mention my brother, you know?

148
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,799
Fine.

149
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,120
You're really capable.

150
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:47,320
All the cops in Chudong combined aren't as capable as you, Lin Wei.

151
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:47,880
Okay.

152
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,920
Then how will you investigate? For how long?

153
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:52,920
One year? Three years? Five years? Ten years? Tell me.

154
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,280
Don't we Guangnan cops need to handle cases?

155
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:57,280
Don't we need to investigate cases?

156
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:01,690
Comrade Lin Wei, Second-Class Merit.

157
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,700
What are you doing?

158
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:07,240
Today, you have to leave with me whether you want to or not.

159
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,000
Get off.

160
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,120
No keys. Let's go.

161
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:10,800
Give me the keys.

162
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,860
What are you doing? Being a hooligan?

163
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,160
Let's go.

164
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:14,880
Give me the keys.

165
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,080
The train is waiting.

166
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,960
Hurry up.

167
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:18,880
Yao Shufen,

168
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,160
where have you been?

169
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:25,040
I've been looking for you for ages.

170
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:26,320
Comrade Yao Shufen.

171
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:29,600
For Nuannuan's sake, you should be more independent.

172
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,250
Perfect, I was looking for you too.

173
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,040
Take a look.

174
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:41,960
Sign it if there are no problems.

175
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:45,560
If you have any questions, call my lawyer.

176
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,520
The business card is inside.

177
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,320
Let me tell you,

178
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:52,120
there is no way you are getting a divorce.

179
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:55,640
You commit domestic violence and visit prostitutes.

180
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:56,760
You treat our home like a hotel,

181
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,090
treat me like a servant,

182
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,920
and even invite wolves into the house.

183
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:01,520
You hurt Nuannuan like that.

184
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,320
Are you even human?

185
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,560
I can't live like this anymore.

186
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,360
Fine.

187
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,400
Stop with this nonsense.

188
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,400
All that nonsense you talked about,

189
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:10,720
do you have evidence for it?

190
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,520
Do you think you can win a lawsuit?

191
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:14,250
The police can testify to this.

192
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:15,920
Officer Ma, Officer Lin,

193
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:18,640
and Officer Zhang are all willing to testify.

194
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,520
Just sign the papers.

195
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:23,120
We're done here.

196
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:24,600
Yao Shufen.

197
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:29,040
Don't forget, we have kids.

198
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,600
Have you considered the kids' feelings?

199
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,600
Would a child want a father like you?

200
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,130
I only have one thing to say anyway.

201
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:46,840
Jinyi, what are you doing?

202
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:49,120
Tell me, did she start it or did I?

203
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:50,800
How about this,

204
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,450
you make her apologize to me right now.

205
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:54,560
Shufen.

206
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:56,320
Shufen.

207
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:08,000
Shufen, you are a woman

208
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,320
with a child.

209
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,200
If you get a divorce,

210
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,120
what will you do then?

211
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:25,040
Go.

212
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,920
You saw it all.

213
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,440
Your daughter started it.

214
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,960
It has nothing to do with me.

215
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:41,160
Don't you think you should discipline her as her father?

216
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:42,360
She even has a child.

217
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:43,720
If she divorces me,

218
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,040
who would want her?

219
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:46,000
I will.

220
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,120
Hong Jinyi.

221
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,400
Sign the papers.

222
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:01,040
I don't care if you drink, whore, and gamble,

223
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:03,370
but you can't treat my daughter like this.

224
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,720
If you don't sign today,

225
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,240
I'll risk my old life.

226
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:09,580
Believe it or not, I'll cripple your other hand too.

227
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:16,720
Shufen.

228
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:21,040
Dad, don't push me.

229
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,400
I can never go back to that house.

230
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:28,770
I've already had Hong Jinyi sign the divorce papers.

231
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,320
Whatever you decide,

232
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,320
I will support you.
